messages.message: Thank you for connecting!  Enjoying NAU?
I did, I graduated in May
Oh excellent.  Find a job already?  I am on the hunt.
Lots to do in Phoenix, I could introduce you to someone if you want?
Want to endorse spam each other?
I am expecting an offer from a place called Vsolvit in Ventura, CA. I'm in southern California so I wanted to find one out here.
Oh SoCo would be nice!  I just had 2 interviews today they went well.  Know any other developers that stuck around AZ?
I'd love to learn more about GIS.
My friend Brandon Paree is at GM in Phoenix
Nice.  I had an interview at Cruise Automation the Google car competitor.  I got to ride in one and pick apart their hardware before Bill Gates.  It was awesome :D
